UPDATED PORTFOLIO
layout: project
title: Updated Linear Actuator Design
description: Updated Drawing Project for ENGRD 2020
technologies: None
---

I decided to design a hexagonal scissor lift to complete this assignment, with a horizontal bar AC fixed to the floor with pins, a moving platform, and 4 links connected to make 2 elbows, creating the hexagonal shape. The top of the actuator is pinned to the midpoint of the moving top platform, while the bottom of the actuator is pinned near the midpoint of the bottom, rigid bar. Base = 1.20 m. L(top) = 1.20 m. Scissor links all the same length l.
